\v 1 \w  [“] I loathe  |strong="5354" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.1" \w* \w  my own  |strong="5315" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.2" \w* \w  life ;  |strong="2416" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.3" \w* \w  I will express  |strong="5800" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.4" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.5" \w* \w  my complaint  |strong="7879" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.6" \w* \w  and speak  |strong="1696" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.7" \w* \w  in the bitterness  |strong="4751" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.8" \w* \w  of my soul .  |strong="5315" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.1.9" \w* \v 2 \w  I will say  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.1" \w* \w  to  |strong="413" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.2" \w* \w  God :  |strong="433" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.3" \w* \w  Do not  |strong="408" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.4" \w* \w  condemn me !  |strong="7561" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.5" \w* \w  Let me know  |strong="3045" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.6" \w* \w  why  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.7" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.8" \w* \w  You prosecute me .  |strong="7378" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.2.9" \w* \v 3 \w  Does it please  |strong="2896" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.1" \w* \w  You  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.2" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.3" \w* \w  to oppress me ,  |strong="6231" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.4" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.5" \w* \w  to reject  |strong="3988" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.6" \w* \w  the work  |strong="3018" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.7" \w* \w  of Your hands  |strong="3709" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.8" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.9" \w* \w  and favor  |strong="3313" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.12" \w* \w  the schemes  |strong="6098" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.10" \w* \w  of the wicked ?  |strong="7563" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.3.11" \w* \v 4 \w  Do You have eyes  |strong="5869" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.1" \w* \w  of flesh  |strong="1320" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.2" \w* \w  ?  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.3" \w* \w  -  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.4" \w* \w  Do You see  |strong="7200" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.5" \w* \w  as man  |strong="582" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.6" \w* \w  sees ?  |strong="7200" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.4.7" \w* \v 5 \w  Are Your days  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.1" \w* \w  like those  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.3" \w* \w  of a [mortal] ,  |strong="582" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.2" \w* \w  or  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.4" \w* \w  Your years  |strong="8141" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.5" \w* \w  like those  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.6" \w* \w  of a man ,  |strong="1397" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.5.7" \w* \v 6 \w  that  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.6.1" \w* \w  You should seek  |strong="1245" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.6.2" \w* \w  my iniquity  |strong="5771" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.6.3" \w* \w  and search out  |strong="1875" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.6.5" \w* \w  my sin —  |strong="2403" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.6.4" \w* \v 7 \w  though  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.1" \w* \w  You know  |strong="1847" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.2" \w* \w  that  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.3" \w* \w  I am not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.4" \w* \w  guilty ,  |strong="7561" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.5" \w* \w  and there is no  |strong="369" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.6" \w* \w  deliverance  |strong="5337" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.8" \w* \w  from Your hand ?  |strong="3027" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.7.7" \w* \v 8 \w  Your hands  |strong="3027" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.1" \w* \w  shaped me  |strong="6087" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.2" \w* \w  and altogether  |strong="3162" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.4" \w* \w  formed me .  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.3" \w* \w  Would You now turn  |strong="5439" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.5" \w* \w  and destroy me ?  |strong="1104" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.8.6" \w* \v 9 \w  Please  |strong="4994" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.9.2" \w* \w  remember  |strong="2142" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.9.1" \w* \w  that  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.9.3" \w* \w  You molded me  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.9.5" \w* \w  like clay .  |strong="2563" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.9.4" \w* \w  Would You 