e  |strong="5352" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.14.6" \w* \w  of my iniquity .  |strong="5771" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.14.4" \w* \v 15 \w  If  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.1" \w* \w  I am guilty ,  |strong="7561" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.2" \w* \w  woe  |strong="480" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.3" \w* \w  to me !  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.4" \w* \w  And even if I am righteous ,  |strong="6663" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.5" \w* \w  I cannot  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.6" \w* \w  lift  |strong="5375" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.7" \w* \w  my head .  |strong="7218" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.8" \w* \w  [I am] full  |strong="7649" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.9" \w* \w  of shame  |strong="7036" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.10" \w* \w  and aware of  |strong="7202" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.11" \w* \w  my affliction .  |strong="6040" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.15.12" \w* \v 16 \w  Should I hold my head high ,  |strong="1342" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.1" \w* \w  You would hunt me  |strong="6679" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.3" \w* \w  like a lion ,  |strong="7826" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.2" \w* \w  and again  |strong="7725" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.4" \w* \w  display Your power  |strong="6381" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.5" \w* \w  against me .  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.16.6" \w* \v 17 \w  You produce new  |strong="2318" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.1" \w* \w  witnesses  |strong="5707" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.2" \w* \w  against me  |strong="5048" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.3" \w* \w  and multiply  |strong="7235" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.4" \w* \w  Your anger  |strong="3708" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.5" \w* \w  toward me .  |strong="5978" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.6" \w* \w  Hardships  |strong="6635" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.8" \w* \w  assault me  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.9" \w* \w  in wave after wave .  |strong="2487" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.17.7" \w* \v 18 \w  Why then  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.18.1" \w* \w  did You bring me  |strong="3318" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.18.3" \w* \w  from the womb ?  |strong="7358" srcloc="WLC:JOB.10.18.2" \w* \w  Oh, that I had died ,  |