\v 1 \w  Then Zophar  |strong="6691" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.1.2" \w* \w  the Naamathite  |strong="5284" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.1.3" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.1.4" \w* \w  replied :  |strong="6030" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.1.1" \w* \v 2 \w  “ Should this stream  |strong="7230" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.1" \w* \w  of words  |strong="1697" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.2" \w* \w  go unanswered  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.3" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="6030" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.4" \w* \w  and such  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.5" \w* \w  a speaker  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.6" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="8193" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.7" \w* \w  be vindicated ?  |strong="6663" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.2.8" \w* \v 3 \w  Should your babbling  |strong="907" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.1" \w* \w  put others  |strong="4962" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.2" \w* \w  to silence ?  |strong="2790" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.3" \w* \w  Will you scoff  |strong="3932" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.4" \w* \w  without  |strong="369" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.5" \w* \w  rebuke ?  |strong="3637" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.3.6" \w* \v 4 \w  You have said ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.1" \w* \w  ‘ My doctrine [is]  |strong="3948" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.3" \w* \w  sound ,  |strong="2134" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.2" \w* \w  and I am  |strong="1961" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.5" \w* \w  pure  |strong="1249" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.4" \w* \w  in Your sight . ’  |strong="5869" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.4.6" \w* \v 5 \w  But  |strong="199" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.1" \w* \w  if only  |strong="4310" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.2" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="5414" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.3" \w* \w  God  |strong="433" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.4" \w* \w  would speak  |strong="1696" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.5" \w* \w  and open  |strong="6605" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.6" \w* \w  His lips  |strong="8193" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.7" \w* \w  against you ,  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.5.8" \w* \v 6 \w  and disclose  |strong="5046" srcloc="WLC:JOB.11.6.1" \w* \w  to you  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.