 |strong="3605" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.10.2" \w* \w  For I will not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.10.6" \w* \w  find  |strong="4672" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.10.7" \w* \w  a wise man  |strong="2450" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.10.9" \w* \w  among you .  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.10.8" \w* \v 11 \w  My days  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.1" \w* \w  have passed ;  |strong="5674" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.2" \w* \w  my plans  |strong="2154" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.3" \w* \w  are broken off —  |strong="5423" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.4" \w* \w  even the desires  |strong="4180" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.5" \w* \w  of my heart .  |strong="3824" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.11.6" \w* \v 12 \w  They have turned  |strong="7760" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.3" \w* \w  night  |strong="3915" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.1" \w* \w  into day ,  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.2" \w* \w  [making] light  |strong="216" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.4" \w* \w  seem near  |strong="7138" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.5" \w* \w  in the face  |strong="6440" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.6" \w* \w  of darkness .  |strong="2822" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.12.7" \w* \v 13 \w  If  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.1" \w* \w  I look  |strong="6960" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.2" \w* \w  for Sheol  |strong="7585" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.3" \w* \w  as my home ,  |strong="1004" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.4" \w* \w  if I spread out  |strong="7502" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.6" \w* \w  my bed  |strong="3326" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.7" \w* \w  in darkness ,  |strong="2822" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.13.5" \w* \v 14 \w  and say  |strong="7121" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.2" \w* \w  to corruption ,  |strong="7845" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.1" \w* \w  ‘ You [are]  |strong="859" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.4" \w* \w  my father , ’  |strong="1" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.3" \w* \w  and to the worm ,  |strong="7415" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.7" \w* \w  ‘ My mother , ’  |strong="517" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.5" \w* \w  or ‘My sister , ’  |strong="269" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.14.6" \w* \v 15 \w  where  |strong="346" srcloc="WLC:JOB.17.15.1"