ower ?  |strong="3581" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.2" \w* \w  No ,  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.5" \w* \w  He  |strong="1931" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.7" \w* \w  would certainly  |strong="389" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.6" \w* \w  take [note]  |strong="7760" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.8" \w* \w  of me .  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.6.9" \w* \v 7 \w  Then  |strong="8033" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.1" \w* \w  an upright man  |strong="3477" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.2" \w* \w  could reason  |strong="3198" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.3" \w* \w  with Him ,  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.4" \w* \w  and I would be delivered  |strong="6403" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.5" \w* \w  forever  |strong="5331" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.6" \w* \w  from my Judge .  |strong="8199" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.7.7" \w* \v 8 \w  If  |strong="2005" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.1" \w* \w  I go  |strong="1980" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.3" \w* \w  east ,  |strong="6924" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.2" \w* \w  He is not there ,  |strong="369" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.4" \w* \w  and if I go west ,  |strong="268" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.5" \w* \w  I cannot  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.6" \w* \w  find  |strong="995" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.7" \w* \w  Him .  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.8.8" \w* \v 9 \w  When He is at work  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.2" \w* \w  in the north ,  |strong="8040" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.1" \w* \w  I cannot  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.3" \w* \w  behold [Him] ;  |strong="2372" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.4" \w* \w  when He turns  |strong="5848" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.5" \w* \w  to the south ,  |strong="3225" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.6" \w* \w  I cannot  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.7" \w* \w  see [Him] .  |strong="7200" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.9.8" \w* \v 10 \w  Yet  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.1" \w* \w  He knows  |strong="3045" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.2" \w* \w  the way I have taken  |strong="1870" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.3" \w* \w  . . . ;  |strong="5978" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.4" \w* \w  when He has tested me ,  |strong="974" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.5" \w* \w  I will come forth  |strong="3318" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.7" \w* \w  as gold .  |strong="2091" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.10.6" \w* \v 11 \w  My feet  |strong="7272" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.3" \w* \w  have followed  |strong="270" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.2" \w* \w  in His tracks ;  |strong="838" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.1" \w* \w  I have kept  |strong="8104" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.5" \w* \w  His way  |strong="1870" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.4" \w* \w  without  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.6" \w* \w  turning aside .  |strong="5186" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.11.7" \w* \v 12 \w  I have not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.3" \w* \w  departed  |strong="4185" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.4" \w* \w  from the command  |strong="4687" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.1" \w* \w  of His lips ;  |strong="8193" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.2" \w* \w  I have treasured  |strong="6845" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.6" \w* \w  the words  |strong="561" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.7" \w* \w  of His mouth  |strong="6310" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.8" \w* \w  more than my daily bread .  |strong="2706" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.12.5" \w* \v 13 \w  But He is unchangeable  |strong="1931" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.1" \w* \w  . . . ,  |strong="259" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.2" \w* \w  and who  |strong="4310" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.3" \w* \w  can oppose Him ?  |strong="7725" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.4" \w* \w  He does  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.7" \w* \w  what He  |strong="5315" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.5" \w* \w  desires .  |strong="183" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.13.6" \w* \v 14 \w  For  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.1" \w* \w  He carries out  |strong="7999" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.2" \w* \w  His decree against me ,  |strong="2706" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.3" \w* \w  and He has  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.6" \w* \w  many  |strong="7227" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.5" \w* \w  such plans .  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.14.4" \w* \v 15 \w  Therefore  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.1" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="3651" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.2" \w* \w  I am terrified  |strong="926" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.4" \w* \w  in His presence ;  |strong="6440" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.3" \w* \w  when I consider this ,  |strong="995" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.5" \w* \w  I fear  |strong="6342" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.6" \w* \w  Him .  |strong="4480" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.15.7" \w* \v 16 \w  God  |strong="410" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.16.1" \w* \w  has made my heart  |strong="3820" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.16.3" \w* \w  faint ;  |strong="7401" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.16.2" \w* \w  the Almighty  |strong="7706" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.16.4" \w* \w  has terrified me .  |strong="926" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.16.5" \w* \v 17 \w  Yet  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.1" \w* \w  I am not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.2" \w* \w  silenced  |strong="6789" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.3" \w* \w  by  |strong="6440" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.4" \w* \w  the darkness ,  |strong="2822" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.5" \w* \w  by the thick darkness  |strong="652" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.8" \w* \w  that covers  |strong="3680" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.7" \w* \w  my face . [’’]  |strong="6440" srcloc="WLC:JOB.23.17.6" \w* 
