\s Elihu Recalls God’s Justice
\p
\v 1 \w  And Elihu  |strong="453" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.1.2" \w* \w  went on  |strong="6030" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.1.1" \w* \w  to say :  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.1.3" \w* \v 2 \w  “ Do you think  |strong="2803" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.2" \w* \w  this  |strong="2063" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.1" \w* \w  is just ?  |strong="4941" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.3" \w* \w  You say ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.4" \w* \w  ‘ I am more righteous  |strong="6664" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.5" \w* \w  than God .’  |strong="410" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.2.6" \w* \v 3 \w  For  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.1" \w* \w  you ask ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.2" \w* \w  ‘ What  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.3" \w* \w  does it profit  |strong="5532" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.4" \w* \w  me ,  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.5" \w* \w  and what  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.6" \w* \w  benefit do I gain  |strong="3276" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.7" \w* \w  apart from sin ?’  |strong="2403" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.3.8" \w* \v 4 \w  I  |strong="589" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.1" \w* \w  will reply  |strong="7725" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.2" \w* \w  to you  |strong="4405" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.3" \w* \w  -  |strong="853" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.4" \w* \w  and to your friends  |strong="7453" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.5" \w* \w  as well .  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.4.6" \w* \v 5 \w  Look  |strong="5027" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.1" \w* \w  to the heavens  |strong="8064" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.2" \w* \w  and see ;  |strong="7200" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.3" \w* \w  gaze  |strong="7789" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.4" \w* \w  at the clouds  |strong="7834" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.5" \w* \w  high  |strong="1361" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.6" \w* \w  above you .  |strong="4480" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.5.7" \w* \v 6 \w  If  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.1" \w* \w  you sin ,  |strong="2398" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.2" \w* \w  what  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.3" \w* \w  do you accomplish  |strong="6466" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.4" \w* \w  against Him ?  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.5" \w* \w  If you multiply  |strong="7231" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.6" \w* \w  your transgressions ,  |strong="6588" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.7" \w* \w  what  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.8" \w* \w  do you do  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.9" \w* \w  to Him ?  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.6.10" \w* \v 7 \w  If  |strong="518" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.1" \w* \w  you are righteous ,  |strong="6663" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.2" \w* \w  what  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.3" \w* \w  do you give  |strong="5414" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.4" \w* \w  Him ,  |srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.5" \w* \w  or  |strong="176" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.6" \w* \w  what  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.7" \w* \w  does He receive  |strong="3947" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.9" \w* \w  from your hand ?  |strong="3027" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.7.8" \w* \v 8 \w  Your wickedness  |strong="7562" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.3" \w* \w  affects only a man  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.1" \w* \w  like yourself ,  |strong="3644" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.2" \w* \w  and your righteousness  |strong="6666" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.6" \w* \w  only a son  |strong="1121" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.4" \w* \w  of man .  |strong="120" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.8.5" \w* \v 9 \w  Men cry out  |strong="2199" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.3" \w* \w  under great  |strong="7230" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.1" \w* \w  oppression ;  |strong="6217" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.2" \w* \w  they plead for relief  |strong="7768" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.4" \w* \w  from the arm  |strong="2220" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.5" \w* \w  of the mighty .  |strong="7227" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.9.6" \w* \v 10 \w  But no  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.1" \w* \w  one asks ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.2" \w* \w  ‘ Where [is]  |strong="346" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.3" \w* \w  God  |strong="433" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.4" \w* \w  my Maker ,  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.5" \w* \w  who gives us  |strong="5414" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.6" \w* \w  songs  |strong="2158" srcloc="WLC:JOB.35.10.7" \